Janówek  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Tolkmicko, within Elbląg County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south-west of Tolkmicko,  north of Elbląg, and  north-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
